      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ICE AGE (8) has a terrific record here with nine wins and two placings from 11 starts. Comes off a (16.64) win last time, scoring by one length in a OPEN over 300m at this track. Looks a leading chance on best. TAKE THE STEPS (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (25.80) in a Grade 3/4/5 at Murray Bridge. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and nine minor placings to his credit. Worth following up. LIFE'S A JOURNEY (2) steps out for the first time at this course. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 5.5 lengths (23.28) at Murray Bridge. Solid formlines coming through his last run. One of the better hopes. BRISTOL MOSS (4) jumps at a shorter trip and still warrants respect.",
